reviewText: Of course on VHS the quality ca not be too good. You want to watch this only if you have seen it in your childhood.

The Circus Angel is a delightful, fanciful movie the whole family can enjoy. The cinematography and sound track are brilliant, and the English dubbing track is the best I've ever seen for a foreign film.  Definitely worth a look!  A.A. Riley, Author of The Key of Aramath.
